# ── Security ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The password hash generator must never be committed to the public repo.
# It does not contain the real password, but its presence signals that
# someone might be generating hashes — and it could be used to test
# guesses against the hash in config.js.
tools/generate-password-hash.html

